{"tid":1576023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個和理非對運動反思","createTime":"2019-09-17T05:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T05:36:57.000Z","uid":51293,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8435f25b7791426aa48db01834ee887daebf64bf","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係一個和理非，我冇ACC所以叫朋友代Post。整場運動入面我做緊只係冷氣軍師、有不反對通知書的集會及遊行同埋係屋企附近接放學。因為我嘅底線係不犯法，而我都知道香港人有唔少都仲係企在不犯法嘅線前面。<br />\n<br />\n想講今次運動咁成功全賴著香港人嘅急速進化，加上團結。但運動發展至今，我諗大家都發現去到一定既樽頸位置，而呢個樽頸位就係在於對方已經跟上左抗爭者嘅進化節奏。警察行動由初期真係只為驅散到後來濫捕、濫捕、濫權、警黑勾結等等，完完全全將佢地黑暗一面喺香港人面前表露無遺，特別係選擇性執法。而我地一直見到係勇武不斷進化，不斷尋求新方法去保護香港人，守護著香港人最後一條防線。<br />\n<br />\n不過時至今日，和理非進化完全停左咁，我先分析一下進化情形比大家睇：<br />\n文宣嘅開始&rarr;長輩圖&rarr;派傳單&rarr;Airdrop&rarr;連儂牆&rarr;聯署&rarr;接放學車隊&rarr;有反對通知書都照遊行集會<br />\n就係咁樣，和理非停暫時停低左，而再分析一下勇武進化情形：<br />\n文宣嘅開始&rarr;口罩&rarr;頭盔&rarr;Road Block&rarr;豬咀&rarr;冰袖&rarr;Full Gear&rarr;自製防具及武器&rarr;滅煙隊&rarr;快閃&rarr;打狗救人&rarr;火魔法&rarr;藍屍仆親<br />\n分析完，大家見到係勇武嘅進化情況明顯地比和理非多幾個階段。記住唔係要割，係要認清自己所在位置同埋可以做到嘅野，特別和理非嘅大家請跟上進化速度。<br />\n<br />\n以下係和理非建議<br />\n第一：遊行時見到有勇武上Gear，請你地立刻！係立刻加快腳步！你行快嘅每一步，就等於令到勇武能夠全身而退機會多一分！（請大家記住濾灌係消耗品，每呼吸一下都係錢，所以唔會無啦啦入濾灌、上豬咀）<br />\n解釋：勇武由頭到尾做嘅野係「保護」，係不惜任何代價咁保護每一個佢希望保護嘅人（支持今次運動嘅人同價值觀（民主與自由）！佢地見到仍然有支持呢場運動嘅和理非將會面臨危險佢地先會上Gear。<br />\n第二：如有藍屍襲擊請試試呢個行動程序，收埋電話＞開遮＞退後等勇武上前＞圍埋去＞藍屍仆親之後散。<br />\n解釋：如果你今日仍然係相信和勇不割，你就要相信佢地會保護你，而你都要盡你嘅責任去保護佢地。收電話係「自己不留任何影像證據」，開遮同圍係「阻擋他人留下任何影像證據」，一齊散係盡方法保護所有手足離開現場。<br />\n第三：認清自己其實根本係冇被捕覺悟，冇受傷覺悟，請你地唔好再睇熱鬧！冇Gear嘅你就走！唔好認為自己安全就得，請你為前線著想！<br />\n解釋：所有前線都唔會放低任何人，齊上齊落係大原則，因為你睇戲而搞到前線冇得走最後被捕同毒打，你對唔對得住保護緊你嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n而家係勇武建議（我完全未上過前線，只係按自己見到嘅野講）<br />\n第一：請你最少搵一個和理非同你組隊<br />\n解釋：當你要上Gear，你嘅和理非隊友就會知咩事，你可以將你身上物品交比佢地保管，而佢地可以幫手呼籲其他唔知情嘅和理非行快幾步，你地可以比較輕裝上陣，行動力加倍。另外係如果你和理非隊友係事情完結後搵唔番你，佢可以即刻幫你搵星光。<br />\n第二：對付敵人時請快、狠、準。<br />\n解釋：你對付無論係狗定福建佬，你都係想佢退，想救人，特別尋日北角一班手足見到福建佬仆親過去扶起佢地嘅時候，打中要害更為重要。中左要害唔死一身潺，達到目的之餘可以更快退，要喺對方支援黎到之前完成任務。<br />\n第三：緊記初心，我地係守護緊香港，亦都請愛惜自己<br />\n解釋：該還手就還手，唔好傻更更比人攻擊唔保護自己，但係只出於「保護」先出手，如果唔係我地就同福建幫冇分別。另外勇武手足其實隨時都可以變番做和理非，請你地必要時休息！保護番自己身體！我地和理非冇左你地係唔得架！要食飽飯！要睇醫生！唔開心要搵樹窿！而呢Ｄ野都係我地一班和理非可以為你地做到嘅野！比飽飯你食！陪你睇醫生！做樹窿聽你地講野！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住各位，因為借朋友acc出post所以變左長文，最後總結，大家睇到進化開始第一步，無論係前線定和理非都好，都係由文宣做第一步，請大家唔好睇少文宣威力，成日驚乜野民意，只要文宣做得好，民意就會企係我地到！另外就係請大家緊記「兄弟爬山，各自努力」，縱使唱歌同人鏈唔會得到勝利，起碼都能夠令香港人記得呢場運動仍未完結。縱使勇武有做得唔夠好嘅時候，請大家平心靜氣，嘗試互相提點，一齊進步甚至進化。互相嘅指責只會造成分化同瓦解，最後內耗而戰敗。<br />\n<br />\n最後加多句，我係一個基督徒，我每日都有為到前線每一個祈禱，雖然我仍然見到有好多慘痛畫面，但你地每一個我都會記在心中，為你地大大力祈禱。<br />\n願主賜福香港！"},{"pid":"2177da7f65b2f2836da479aa29fc1986dada2c43","tid":1576023,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ee8e6179dc978fcd325dc2f20f5931d349976e1","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"568a63490136eac39f164529097233136c77bfc5","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"bfa1b440793d1ab40a452b3f798d16d3ffce5f86","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"9281259b4e1b66e09b7ffae4eb9d17b45c4fae86","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"7e6e5b3a8bef80b858cc74c3c77a43140cd819cf","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"cb16d7484852997ccab788df0dcfc0912e6068f6","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:17:01.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"66737fde6e34e7faaa8a52c21be84d6ee520c64d","tid":1576023,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"打狗救人"},{"pid":"6933e8a686493bc496d36721861bb630a75d6fc9","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"0e891ded90514b5219ef46f241cdfede9e2d9c18","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"e8428a8830f1234c93d8d33412fffa3b99c6d33b","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"028022b02c87522701620105ca36d9c8c57c3e37","tid":1576023,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"組隊自衛"},{"pid":"f6e512c51a2204881078e53ec61d03b3b4a0e879","tid":1576023,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"自推 10/10"},{"pid":"5f012a5f93d8596f1b6f1e2d6225cf074fbe2263","tid":1576023,"uid":320135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"其實點解和理非一定係唔犯法，和平集會，塗鴉呢啲都係和理非嘅行為嚟，並唔係和理非一定唔可以犯法喎"},{"pid":"123057288d55baa5b7fef9ba6ad5272198c678c9","tid":1576023,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbtyWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStbtyWY.jpg&h=a80df56a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span> 約定你</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=3fbb07ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e730faa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全面升級：私了、暗戰、快閃、滲透、狗仔隊</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572762</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推爆佢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8fd6c0b63b4c60d55b588486208b6e1b421f1950","tid":1576023,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB/TG搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想支持某間發國難財的五金鋪,但又唔方便親自落去買水買衫? 入黎喇</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1573714/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1573714/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"b2cc2f39ffcc987d75031e470ebb773386458a51","tid":1576023,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:36:57.000Z","msg":"最無進化就係啲仆街和理非囉"}]}